description.narrative: This activity (Support to Humanitarian Surge Staff) is a component of Humanitarian Assistance in Response to Pakistan Floods 2010 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £1,740,965. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Relief co-ordination and support services. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 19-08-2010 and the end date is 30-06-2012.
